casebody.data:
Adrienne I. HARROW, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Martha HARROW, etc., et al., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2120 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 13, 2018 LOGUE, LUCK and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Following review of appellees' answer brief and motion for clarification, it is ordered that the above styled appeal is hereby dismissed for failure to file an initial brief pursuant to Florida Rule of Appellate Procedure 9.210.
